WEBVTT

00:02.170 --> 00:03.104
♪ Da, da, da-ba-da, da, da,
ba-da-ba-da-ba ♪

00:04.738 --> 00:06.207
♪ Da, da, da-ba-da, da, da
Let's go!

00:06.240 --> 00:08.076
♪ We'll be there

00:08.109 --> 00:10.578
♪ A wink and a smile
and a great old time ♪

00:10.611 --> 00:12.980
♪ Yeah, we'll be there

00:13.013 --> 00:15.049
♪ Wherever we are,
there's some fun to be found ♪

00:15.083 --> 00:17.185
♪ We'll be there
when you turn that corner ♪

00:17.218 --> 00:18.519
♪ We'll jump out the bush

00:18.552 --> 00:20.254
♪ With a big bear hug
and a smile ♪

00:20.288 --> 00:21.455
♪ We'll be there

00:23.457 --> 00:29.197
♪♪

00:29.230 --> 00:31.065
Welp,
that's the last of it.

00:31.099 --> 00:33.934
Your family sure has a lot of
Christmas decorations, Chloe.

00:33.967 --> 00:36.204
Eh, Christmas is kind of
a big deal in my neighborhood.

00:36.237 --> 00:38.339
Yeah, no kidding.

00:38.372 --> 00:40.874
Thank you, guys, so much for
helping me decorate the house.

00:40.908 --> 00:43.411
For the first time, Mom let me
handle the decorations,

00:43.444 --> 00:46.947
which means I get
to pick the tree!

00:46.980 --> 00:51.385
Finally, after 12 years
of having horrible trees...

00:51.419 --> 00:53.287
like my first
disappointing tree.

00:53.321 --> 00:55.323
Honey,
the perfect tree!

00:58.259 --> 01:00.461
Or the nuclear tree
four years ago.

01:00.494 --> 01:04.365
The perfect tree!

01:04.398 --> 01:07.301
And then there was
last year's disaster.

01:07.335 --> 01:09.770
[ Speaks foreign language ]
The perfect tree!

01:09.803 --> 01:11.372
[ Electricity crackles ]
Ooh!

01:11.405 --> 01:14.308
[ All screaming ]

01:14.342 --> 01:16.244
[ Shudders ]

01:16.277 --> 01:17.811
But this year
will be different

01:17.845 --> 01:19.380
because we're going
to find the best tree

01:19.413 --> 01:21.815
in the whole dang forest!

01:21.849 --> 01:23.251
Let's go!
Let's go! Let's go!

01:23.284 --> 01:24.452
Ice Bear will drive.

01:24.485 --> 01:26.086
Bye, guys. Have fun!

01:26.120 --> 01:27.955
So we'll leave everything
here for you two!

01:27.988 --> 01:30.090
We'll be back soon!
Okay.

01:30.124 --> 01:33.561
Don't worry. We'll do
an amazing job with the house.

01:33.594 --> 01:36.264
All right. Let's get
this party started.

01:36.297 --> 01:38.098
[ Grunts ] Huh?

01:38.132 --> 01:40.134
[ Grunts ]

01:42.136 --> 01:44.805
This might take a while.

01:44.838 --> 01:47.975
♪♪

01:48.008 --> 01:51.111
Oh, this is going to
be so fun!

01:51.145 --> 01:53.113
I can't wait to find
the perfect Christmas tree.

01:53.147 --> 01:55.983
Aren't you excited? Ice Bear
is excited to chop something.

01:57.117 --> 01:59.153
Oh, look. Snow!
I haven't seen snow in forever!

01:59.187 --> 02:00.621
♪ Christmas time is ringing

02:00.654 --> 02:02.122
So pretty.

02:02.156 --> 02:04.992
♪ The jingle bells
so bright ♪

02:05.025 --> 02:08.329
♪ Ho, ho, ho,
and lots of snow ♪

02:08.362 --> 02:11.599
♪ What a joyous sight

02:11.632 --> 02:14.435
We're here! We're here!
We're here! Wow! We're here!

02:14.468 --> 02:17.037
Snow! Snow! Snow!

02:17.070 --> 02:18.972
[ Groans ]

02:19.006 --> 02:22.176
Snow! [ Chuckles ]

02:22.210 --> 02:24.378
Ice Bear sees a sign --
a turkey sign.

02:24.412 --> 02:26.480
Turkeys?

02:26.514 --> 02:30.150
"Beware of wild turkeys"?
Do you think they're dangerous?

02:30.184 --> 02:34.388
Nothing is more dangerous than
Ice Bear, except Ice Bear.

02:34.422 --> 02:36.290
Good point. Let's go.

02:36.324 --> 02:40.561
♪♪

02:40.594 --> 02:42.363
Is this the tree?

02:42.396 --> 02:44.998
Hmm. Nope. Not it.

02:45.032 --> 02:48.202
No. Nope, nope.
Definitely not.

02:48.236 --> 02:51.205
Hmm, finding the perfect tree is
going to be harder than I thought.

02:51.239 --> 02:53.241
How does Chloe
know perfect tree?

02:53.274 --> 02:56.009
The perfect tree?
Hmm.

02:56.043 --> 03:00.180
Well, when you see it, you
just kind of know, you know?

03:00.214 --> 03:04.352
Ice Bear knows.
Ice Bear has been in love.

03:04.385 --> 03:07.888
Then you know exactly what
I'm talking about because...

03:07.921 --> 03:11.024
♪ When you want to
find the perfect ♪

03:11.058 --> 03:14.228
♪ Magical Christmas tree

03:14.262 --> 03:17.365
♪ All you have to do
to find it ♪

03:17.398 --> 03:20.501
♪ Is use your compass heart,
you see ♪

03:20.534 --> 03:26.073
♪ Snowflakes dance
all around ♪

03:26.106 --> 03:29.277
♪ Come you,
you know, you can ♪

03:29.310 --> 03:32.680
♪ Find anything,
you know you can ♪

03:32.713 --> 03:36.216
♪ Dreams are sprinkled
far and wide ♪

03:36.250 --> 03:41.088
♪ Across the land

03:41.121 --> 03:44.525
♪♪

03:44.558 --> 03:46.594
Hmm. Too tall.

03:46.627 --> 03:49.463
Way too small.

03:51.432 --> 03:54.468
Eh.
Same size as me -- scary.

03:54.502 --> 03:56.537
Here,
put me on your shoulders.

03:56.570 --> 03:59.206
♪♪

03:59.239 --> 04:00.574
[ Gasps ]
What's that over there?

04:00.608 --> 04:02.242
Let's go!

04:02.276 --> 04:07.080
♪♪

04:07.114 --> 04:08.516
Aah!

04:10.117 --> 04:12.085
Boo.
Aah!

04:12.119 --> 04:23.297
♪♪

04:23.331 --> 04:26.099
Well, it took us two hours, but
we finally untangled the lights.

04:26.133 --> 04:28.101
[ Chuckles ] Now we've got to
put them on the roof.

04:28.135 --> 04:30.738
Leave it to me.
Super Christmas light toss!

04:30.771 --> 04:33.441
Dude, why?

04:33.474 --> 04:36.444
Hey, how's the snow
coming along, Grizz?

04:36.477 --> 04:40.481
[ Chuckles ] Great. I just
finished my last can of snow.

04:40.514 --> 04:42.450
Grizz, that was
for the entire house!

04:42.483 --> 04:44.251
Ah.

04:44.284 --> 04:48.456
♪ Bells on bob tails ring,
making spirits bright ♪

04:48.489 --> 04:50.691
Oop. [ Chuckles ]

04:50.724 --> 04:53.126
Oh.
♪ Oh, what fun

04:53.160 --> 04:55.295
Come on. Okay.
♪ To laugh and sing

04:55.329 --> 04:56.664
♪ A sleighing song tonight

04:56.697 --> 04:58.131
[ Groans ]

04:58.165 --> 04:59.333
I'm going to
say this again,

04:59.367 --> 05:01.001
but this is a bad idea.

05:01.034 --> 05:02.336
Ha!
This is going to be great!

05:02.370 --> 05:03.637
Ho, ho, ho, ho!

05:03.671 --> 05:05.272
Merry Christmas!

05:05.305 --> 05:07.040
Ho, ho, ho, ho!

05:07.074 --> 05:08.342
Oh, no.

05:08.376 --> 05:10.344
[ Siren wails ]

05:10.378 --> 05:15.115
Fireman Paul: Don't worry. We'll
get you down. Just grab my hand.

05:15.148 --> 05:16.484
Grizzly: I'm not stuck!

05:16.517 --> 05:18.285
Ugh,
I'm sorry about this.

05:18.318 --> 05:20.153
Eh, it happens
all the time.

05:20.187 --> 05:21.522
It's usually just
raccoons, though.

05:21.555 --> 05:23.424
[ Laughs ]

05:25.526 --> 05:27.361
[ Turkey gobbles ]
Stop.

05:27.395 --> 05:29.497
Ice Bear heard something.

05:29.530 --> 05:33.333
[ Turkey gobbling ]

05:33.367 --> 05:38.038
♪♪

05:38.071 --> 05:39.339
Huh.
Ugh.

05:39.373 --> 05:41.341
Turkeys are
so weird-looking.

05:41.375 --> 05:44.412
[ Turkey gobbling ]

05:44.445 --> 05:47.314
♪♪

05:47.347 --> 05:49.650
Whoa, why is he
walking onto the ice?

05:49.683 --> 05:51.652
Wait, Ice Bear
knows this joke.

05:51.685 --> 05:54.354
Why did turkey cross the ice?
Why?

05:54.388 --> 05:56.323
To get to other side.

05:56.356 --> 05:58.392
Turkey, no!
Chloe, stay.

05:58.426 --> 06:09.269
♪♪

06:09.302 --> 06:11.539
Is he okay?
Ice Bear thinks so.

06:11.572 --> 06:14.542
Quick, give him mouth-to-mouth
-- or mouth-to-beak!

06:14.575 --> 06:16.410
[ Turkey gobbles ]
Aah!

06:18.579 --> 06:20.614
[ Turkey gobbles ]

06:20.648 --> 06:23.584
Hey! Come on!
He's getting away!

06:23.617 --> 06:26.386
Get back here, turkey!

06:26.420 --> 06:29.557
And done! Perfect!

06:29.590 --> 06:31.224
Do you think this
industrial glue will hold?

06:31.258 --> 06:33.527
Totally. This stuff
is permanent.

06:33.561 --> 06:35.896
They did want these up here
permanently, right?

06:35.929 --> 06:39.299
Whoa, Grizz, great job
on inflating the snowman.

06:39.332 --> 06:41.535
Thanks, bro.
I do what I can.

06:41.569 --> 06:44.404
Did you use helium?

06:44.438 --> 06:47.374
Hmm, I think we're
missing some letters.

06:47.407 --> 06:49.443
Oh, no, no, no.
They're just down here. See?

06:49.477 --> 06:51.244
♪ Bells on bob tails ring

06:51.278 --> 06:52.746
Well, that's everything.

06:52.780 --> 06:55.315
Yep, that is everything.

06:55.348 --> 06:56.550
Too much?

06:56.584 --> 06:57.918
Nah, come on.

06:57.951 --> 07:00.721
♪ Oh, what fun to
laugh and sing ♪

07:00.754 --> 07:02.255
[ Growls ]

07:02.289 --> 07:04.825
[ Turkey gobbling ]

07:04.858 --> 07:07.260
Ugh!
What's his problem?

07:07.294 --> 07:10.130
Hmph! That's the thanks you get
for saving his life.

07:10.163 --> 07:12.900
"Beware of turkeys"? Yeah.
Beware of their attitude.

07:12.933 --> 07:15.268
Chloe, look.
Huh?

07:15.302 --> 07:17.738
[ Gasps ]
Look at that.

07:17.771 --> 07:20.140
[ Turkey gobbles ]

07:20.173 --> 07:22.776
I -- I think that's it.

07:22.810 --> 07:24.444
Come on.

07:26.446 --> 07:28.916
♪ Could it be

07:28.949 --> 07:32.419
♪ The perfect tree?

07:32.452 --> 07:35.589
♪ Oh, my gosh

07:35.623 --> 07:37.558
It is.

07:39.493 --> 07:41.662
Ice Bear likes.

07:43.196 --> 07:45.232
Chloe Park likes, too.

07:46.734 --> 07:49.637
Cut it down.

07:49.670 --> 07:52.305
[ Grunting ]

07:52.339 --> 07:55.809
♪♪

07:55.843 --> 07:58.345
Oh!
Oh, my gosh, finally!

08:00.313 --> 08:02.482
[ Pants, grunts ]

08:02.516 --> 08:04.518
Ha!
The perfect tree is mine!

08:04.552 --> 08:05.986
Ha ha ha!

08:06.019 --> 08:08.522
Ice Bear impressed with
Chloe's tree location skills.

08:08.556 --> 08:10.891
Let's get this tree home.
I can't wait to show Dad.

08:10.924 --> 08:12.325
Huh? Wha?

08:12.359 --> 08:13.827
Aah!

08:13.861 --> 08:15.228
Chloe.

08:15.262 --> 08:17.665
Aah!

08:17.698 --> 08:20.534
♪♪

08:20.568 --> 08:22.703
Aah!

08:22.736 --> 08:25.338
[ Screaming ]

08:25.372 --> 08:31.745
♪♪

08:31.779 --> 08:33.981
Ice Bear will save you.

08:34.014 --> 08:36.216
[ Grunts ]
Aah!

08:36.249 --> 08:39.887
♪♪

08:39.920 --> 08:41.521
Huh? Aah!

08:41.555 --> 08:43.724
Aah!

08:43.757 --> 08:45.392
Ugh!

08:46.560 --> 08:48.028
Chloe, climb up.

08:48.061 --> 08:50.363
O-okay.

08:51.765 --> 08:53.601
Ah! [ Whimpers ]

08:53.634 --> 08:56.904
♪♪

08:56.937 --> 08:58.538
Grab Ice Bear's paw.

08:58.572 --> 09:01.875
[ Grunting ]

09:01.909 --> 09:03.777
Aah!

09:07.748 --> 09:10.283
Is Chloe okay?

09:10.317 --> 09:13.020
♪♪

09:13.053 --> 09:14.454
Thanks.

09:14.487 --> 09:16.389
[ Gasps ]
Wait, the tree!

09:16.423 --> 09:21.629
Oh, no! The perfect tree,
it's -- it's gone.

09:21.662 --> 09:23.296
Ohh!

09:23.330 --> 09:25.565
Ice Bear will chop down
whole forest for Chloe.

09:25.599 --> 09:28.902
No, it's okay. That was
the only tree for me.

09:28.936 --> 09:31.304
Let's just go home.

09:31.338 --> 09:32.606
[ Turkey gobbles ]
Huh?

09:34.975 --> 09:36.476
[ Turkey gobbles ]

09:36.509 --> 09:38.545
Oh, it's that turkey.

09:38.578 --> 09:40.981
[ Turkeys gobbling ]

09:41.014 --> 09:43.416
Huh, that must be
its flock.

09:43.450 --> 09:47.454
[ Turkeys gobbling ]

09:49.657 --> 09:51.458
What -- what
are they doing?

09:51.491 --> 09:54.294
[ Gobbling continues ]

09:54.327 --> 09:58.799
♪♪

09:58.832 --> 10:01.835
Oh! Stop!

10:01.869 --> 10:03.771
[ Gobbling continues ]

10:03.804 --> 10:05.572
Turkeys, no!

10:05.605 --> 10:07.641
No, not the turkeys, too!

10:07.675 --> 10:09.677
What is happening? Ah!

10:10.944 --> 10:12.780
[ Gobbling continues ]
Huh?

10:12.813 --> 10:17.517
♪♪

10:17.550 --> 10:19.820
[ Gasps ] They saved the tree
for us!

10:19.853 --> 10:21.689
Wait, turkeys can fly?

10:21.722 --> 10:24.457
Ice Bear has never seen
such majestic creatures.

10:24.491 --> 10:28.862
♪♪

10:28.896 --> 10:32.632
Thank you, turkeys!
We'll never forget you!

10:34.702 --> 10:44.712
♪♪

10:44.745 --> 10:49.917
And done!
Presenting the perfect tree!

10:52.052 --> 10:54.021
That is the perfect tree.

10:54.054 --> 10:56.489
Oh, speaking of perfect...

10:56.523 --> 10:58.025
[ Electricity crackles ]

10:58.058 --> 11:00.828
Merry Christmas!
